data.description: Welcome to your dream log home nestled in amongst the towering pines. This remarkable property offers a perfect blend of rustic charm and modern comfort. Located on a spacious 3.75 acre lot, this 3 bedroom, 2 bath log home boasts a tranquil environment creating a picturesque retreat for outdoor enthusiasts. As you approach the property, you'll be greeted by a large wraparound deck, providing the ideal space to relax and entertain. Stepping inside, you'll be impressed by the warm and cozy ambiance highlighted by the knotty pine finishes throughout. The main floor features an open concept kitchen, living, and dining area all complemented by cathedral ceilings that create an airy and spacious feel. Also on the main floor, you will find a convenient mudroom offering ample storage for outdoor gear. Additionally, there are 2 bedrooms and a full bath on this level. Upstairs you will find the master suite with a private bath, and an open loft area offering versatility to use as a sitting area or an excellent spot for a home office. The partially finished basement provides a great space for a game room / family room allowing for indoor recreation and relaxation during inclement weather. Numerous nearby lakes offer opportunities for fishing enthusiasts, while the surrounding wilderness provides the perfect backdrop for hiking, exploring, and connecting with nature. The current owner has recently been offering the home as a vacation rental. Whether you're looking for a permanent residence or vacation retreat, this property offers the perfect escape from the hustle and bustle of city life. Don't miss the chance to make this log home yours! Schedule your showing today!
